{"tid":1122465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山耀安邨起火冒濃煙 冷氣機燒到跌落街","createTime":"2019-04-24T03:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T04:06:15.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"166531c5813b81cf8d116f29dd805e4505636756","tid":1122465,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmdR7qm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmdR7qm.png&h=272fa815&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubX0giH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubX0giH.png&h=03de98bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7j1Xiw3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7j1Xiw3.png&h=2d177df8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soynuDK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsoynuDK.png&h=cb06e104&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2RoYw4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2RoYw4.png&h=fecef511&s={SIZE}\" />冷氣機燒毀跌落地面。讀者陳小姐提供<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/txdKHYL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtxdKHYL.png&h=c8848176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防開喉救火。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n早上10時33分，馬鞍山耀安邨耀謙樓高層一單位，警方接獲多人報案，指單位起火冒煙，火勢猛烈，冒出濃煙，消防接報到場，出動一喉一煙帽隊撲救，起火單位的冷氣機被燒毀，飛墮到地面，幸無擊中途人。火警期間約有30多名居民疏散到安全地方。<br />\n<br />\n讀者陳小姐住在同一幢大廈較高層單位，她說今晨起床後，弟弟嗅到燶味，問她有否燒着雜物，她檢查後發現屋內沒有不妥，探頭窗外，始見樓下數層有單位冒出白煙，當時未見有火，「但冇幾耐就有火光，越燒越犀利，冷氣機都跌落街，好多碎片，我唔知有冇人喺單位，但聽唔到叫救命聲，隔咗一段時間先有火警鐘響起，冇擔心要走火，因隔得遠，亦冇差人、消防或管理員上門叫我哋疏散。消防到場架起雲梯救火。」"},{"pid":"2edcd426e08a449fb4dfad50556c5301aab1dd1a","tid":1122465,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"咁會唔會俾人告"},{"pid":"41390df8c52d2ca4f1332cb59a159ed9c4af244e","tid":1122465,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:06:15.000Z","msg":"高空擲物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}